text: Köy Hizmetleri Anadolu Lisesi Istanbul Köy Hizmetleri Anadolu Lisesi (better known as Köy Hizmetleri Anadolu Lisesi) is one of prominent Anatolian High Schools in Turkey. Located in Kartal, a developing part of Istanbul, the school opened for education in 1993.
